# Sūra XXX.: Rūm, or The Roman Empire.

### Section 2

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_011.gif)

11. All<u>a</u>hu yabdao alkhalqa thumma yuAAeeduhu thumma ilayhi
turjaAAoon**a**

11\. It is God Who begins  
(The process of) creation;  
Then repeats it; then  
Shall ye be brought back  
To Him.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_012.gif)

12. Wayawma taqoomu a**l**ss<u>a</u>AAatu yublisu almujrimoon**a**

12\. On the Day that  
The Hour will be established,  
The guilty will be  
Struck dumb with despair.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_013.gif)

13. Walam yakun lahum min shurak<u>a</u>-ihim shufaAA<u>a</u>o
wak<u>a</u>noo bishurak<u>a</u>-ihim k<u>a</u>fireen**a**

13\. No intercessor will they have  
Among their "Partners",  
And they will (themselves)  
Reject their "Partners".

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_014.gif)

14. Wayawma taqoomu a**l**ss<u>a</u>AAatu yawma-i<u>th</u>in
yatafarraqoon**a**

14\. On the Day that  
The Hour will he established,—  
That Day shall (all men)  
Be sorted out.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_015.gif)

15. Faamm<u>a</u> alla<u>th</u>eena <u>a</u>manoo waAAamiloo
a**l**<u>ssa</u>li<u>ha</u>ti fahum fee raw<u>d</u>atin
yu<u>h</u>baroon**a**

15\. Then those who have believed  
And worked righteous deeds,  
Shall be made happy  
In a Mead of Delight.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_016.gif)

16. Waamm<u>a</u> alla<u>th</u>eena kafaroo waka<u>thth</u>aboo
bi-<u>a</u>y<u>a</u>tin<u>a</u> waliq<u>a</u>-i al-<u>a</u>khirati
faol<u>a</u>-ika fee alAAa<u>tha</u>bi mu<u>hd</u>aroon**a**

16\. And those who have rejected  
Faith and falsely denied  
Our Signs and the meeting  
Of the Hereafter,—such  
Shall be brought forth to  
Punishment.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_017.gif)

17. Fasub<u>ha</u>na All<u>a</u>hi <u>h</u>eena tumsoona wa<u>h</u>eena
tu<u>s</u>bi<u>h</u>oon**a**

17\. So (give) glory to God,  
When ye reach eventide  
And when ye rise  
In the morning;

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_018.gif)

18. Walahu al<u>h</u>amdu fee a**l**ssam<u>a</u>w<u>a</u>ti
wa**a**l-ar<u>d</u>i waAAashiyyan wa<u>h</u>eena
tu*<u>th</u>*hiroon**a**

18\. Yea, To Him be praise,  
In the heavens and on earth;  
And in the late afternoon  
And when the day  
Begins to decline.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/030/030_019.gif)

19. Yukhriju al<u>h</u>ayya mina almayyiti wayukhriju almayyita mina
al<u>h</u>ayyi wayu<u>h</u>yee al-ar<u>d</u>a baAAda mawtih<u>a</u>
waka<u>tha</u>lika tukhrajoon**a**

19\. It is He Who brings out  
The living from the dead,  
And brings out the dead  
From the living, and Who  
Gives life to the earth  
After it is dead:  
And thus shall ye be  
Brought out (from the dead).

